The Bank of England said it had giventhe money market a further 485 mln stg assistance in theafternoon session. This takes the Bank's total help so fartoday to 582 mln stg and compares with its forecast of a 750mln stg shortage in the system today.    The central bank bought bank bills outright comprising 345mln stg in band one at 9-7/8 pct and 75 mln stg in band two at9-3/16 pct. It also purchased 65 mln stg of treasury bills inband one at 9-7/8 pct. REUTER&#3;